---
layout: base.njk
title: Articles
description: Read practical SEO and content guides on UD Marketing Tools.
permalink: /articles/
---

<section class="page-hero page-hero-compact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-hero-copy">
      <span class="page-kicker">Articles</span>
      <h1>Practical marketing guides for clearer writing, better SEO, and stronger page performance.</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-lead">
        Explore simple, actionable articles designed to work together with the tools on UD Marketing Tools.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cluster-panel cluster-panel-compact">
      <div class="cluster-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Featured Cluster</span>
        <h2>Campaign tracking guides</h2>
        <p>
          Learn how UTM tracking works, what UTM parameters mean, and how to create tracking URLs for Google Analytics campaigns.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cluster-links">
        <a href="/tools/utm-builder/">Free UTM Builder</a>
        <a href="/articles/what-is-utm-tracking/">What Is UTM Tracking?</a>
        <a href="/articles/what-are-utm-parameters/">What Are UTM Parameters?</a>
        <a href="/articles/how-to-create-a-tracking-url/">How to Create a Tracking URL</a>
        <a href="/articles/how-to-use-utm-builder-for-google-analytics/">How to Use UTM Builder for Google Analytics</a>
        <a href="/articles/utm-builder-vs-campaign-url-builder/">UTM Builder vs Campaign URL Builder</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-tight articles-index-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head section-head-split">
      <div>
        <span class="mini-label">Latest guides</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">All articles</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Browse practical writing, SEO, and content optimization guides pulled automatically from your articles data.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid articles-grid">
      {% for article in articles | reverse %}
      <article class="feature-card article-card article-card-archive">
        <div class="feature-top">
          <span class="feature-tag">Article</span>
          <span class="feature-meta">{{ article.date }}</span>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-body">
          <h3>{{ article.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ article.description }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-bottom">
          <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" href="/articles/{{ article.slug }}/">Read article</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
